entity.description: Forecasters say Tropical Storm Dorian could reach near-hurricane strength as it makes landfall in Puerto Rico on Wednesday.

tweets.text: Tropical-storm-force winds from #Dorian could begin in parts of Florida *as early as* Saturday evening or Saturday night. Now is the time to begin thinking about what kinds of preparations you might need to make over the next couple of days. https://t.co/yChCF6oWL9 https://t.co/sY8jyYVaxz
